## NVIDIA Source Code License

This project integrates **NVIDIA FoundationPose**, which is provided under the NVIDIA Source Code License.

**Affected Components:**
- `vision_pipeline` (may contain FoundationPose integration)

**Important Notice:**

FoundationPose and related components are provided under a separate NVIDIA license. Before distributing this software or creating derivative works that include FoundationPose, you must:

1. Read and accept the terms of the NVIDIA Source Code License
2. Comply with all restrictions and requirements specified in that license

For details, visit: https://github.com/NVlabs/FoundationPose/blob/main/LICENSE

**Copyright:** © NVIDIA Corporation

